<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en"
xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
lang="en" metal:use-macro="context/main_template/macros/master"
i18n:domain="plone">
<body>
<metal:content-core fill-slot="main">
<metal:content-core define-macro="main"
        tal:define="cview nocall:context/@@soercontent_view;">
    <div id="parent-title">
        <h1 id="parent-fieldname-title" class="documentFirstHeading">
            SOER 2015 — The European environment — state and outlook 2015
        </h1>

        <div class="documentDescription">A comprehensive assessment of the European environment's state, trends and prospects, in a global context.
        </div>
    </div>
        <!--? SOER2015 Template-->
        <!--? Tabbed navigation -->
        <div class="top-highlights">
            <ul class="eea-tabs eea-tabs-soer">
                <li><a href="#tab-synthesis-report" id="tab-synthesis-report"><span class="eea-icon eea-icon-clipboard eea-icon-2x"></span>Synthesis report</a></li>
                <li><a href="#tab-global-megatrends" id="tab-global-megatrends"><span class="eea-icon eea-icon-globe eea-icon-2x"></span>Global megatrends</a></li>
                <li><a href="#tab-thematic-briefing" id="tab-thematic-briefing"><span class="eea-icon eea-icon-leaf eea-icon-2x"></span>European briefings</a></li>
                <li><a href="#tab-cross-country-comparisons" id="tab-cross-country-comparisons"><span class="eea-icon eea-icon-bar-chart-o eea-icon-2x"></span>Cross-country comparisons</a></li>
                <li><a href="#tab-regions-countries" id="tab-regions-countries"><span class="eea-icon eea-icon-map-marker eea-icon-2x"></span>Countries<br>and regions</a></li>
            </ul>
            <div class="eea-row">
                <div class="column-area">
                    <div class="eea-tabs-panels eea-tabs-panels-soer">
                        <div class="eea-tabs-panel">
                            <p>The synthesis report informs future European environmental policy in general and its implementation between 2015 and 2020 in particular. It includes a reflection on the European environment in a global context, as well as chapters summarising the state of, trends in, and prospects for the environment in Europe.</p>

                            <div class="eea-list-columns"
                                        tal:define="collection python:context.restrictedTraverse('soer-2015/collections/synthesis', None);"
                                        tal:condition="nocall:collection">
                                     <tal:results tal:define="results python:collection.queryCatalog()"
                                            tal:condition="results">
                                        <ul>
                                            <li tal:repeat="result results">
                                                <a tal:attributes="href result/getURL">
                                                    <span tal:content="result/Title">Title</span>
                                                </a>
                                            </li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </tal:results>
                             </div>


                            <div class="eea-footer-right visualClear pull-right">
                                <div class="visualHidden">
                                    <div id="pdf-choice-synthesis">
                                        <span class="eea-icon eea-icon-download eea-icon-2x"></span> <a href="/soer-2015/synthesis/report/action-download-pdf">Download report (PDF)</a> - on 3rd of March.
                                        <br />
                                        <span class="eea-icon eea-icon-globe eea-icon-2x"></span> <a href="/soer-2015/synthesis/folder_listing">Synthesis in more languages (PDF)</a> - on 3rd of March.
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="visualHidden">
                                    <div id="epub-choice-synthesis">
                                        <span class="eea-icon eea-icon-download eea-icon-2x"></span> <a href="/soer-2015/synthesis/report/action-download-epub">Download report (EPUB)</a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <p class="pull-left">Synthesis report in several languages</p> <a class="download-pdf pull-left fancybox" title="download PDF" href="#pdf-choice-synthesis"><span class="eea-icon eea-icon-file-pdf-o eea-icon-2x"></span></a> <a class="download-epub pull-left fancybox" title="download EPUB" href="#epub-choice-synthesis"><span class="eea-icon eea-icon-mobile-phone eea-icon-3x"></span></a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="eea-tabs-panel">
                            <p>The global megatrends report assesses 11 global megatrends (GMT) of importance for Europe’s environment in the long term. In assessing key drivers, trends and implications for Europe, it aims to provide an improved basis for strategic European environmental policymaking.</p>

                            <tal:global tal:define="results python:cview.content(parent_id='soer-2015', object_id='global')">
                                <ul>
                                    <li tal:repeat="result results">
                                        <a tal:attributes="href result/getURL">
                                            <span tal:content="result/title">Global</span>
                                        </a>
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </tal:global>

                            <div class="eea-footer-right visualClear pull-right">
                                <div class="visualHidden">
                                    <div id="pdf-choice-global">
                                        <span class="eea-icon eea-icon-download eea-icon-2x"></span> <a href="/soer-2015/global/action-download-pdf">Download report (PDF)</a>&nbsp;- Use username/password received via email.
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="visualHidden">
                                    <div id="epub-choice-global">
                                        <span class="eea-icon eea-icon-download eea-icon-2x"></span> <a href="/soer-2015/global/download.epub">Download report (EPUB)</a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                 <p class="pull-left">Download all global megatrends</p>
                                 <a class="download-pdf pull-left" href="/soer-2015/global/download.pdf"  title="download PDF"><span class="eea-icon eea-icon-file-pdf-o eea-icon-2x"></span></a> <a class="download-epub pull-left fancybox"  title="download EPUB" href="#epub-choice-global"><span class="eea-icon eea-icon-mobile-phone eea-icon-3x"></span></a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="eea-tabs-panel">
                            <p>European briefings present the state, recent trends and prospects in 25 key environmental themes, grouped in three clusters: environment; socio-economic; and systemic perspectives.</p>


                            <tal:europe>
                                <div class="eea-list-columns eea-three-columns"
                                        tal:define="collection python:context.restrictedTraverse('soer-2015/collections/environmental-themes', None);"
                                        tal:condition="nocall:collection">
                                    <tal:results tal:define="results python:collection.queryCatalog()"
                                            tal:condition="results">
                                        <h4>Environmental themes</h4>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li tal:repeat="result results">
                                                <a tal:attributes="href result/getURL">
                                                    <span tal:content="result/Title">Title</span>
                                                </a>
                                            </li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </tal:results>
                                </div>

                                <div class="eea-list-columns eea-three-columns"
                                        tal:define="collection python:context.restrictedTraverse('soer-2015/collections/socio-economic-dimensions', None);"
                                        tal:condition="nocall:collection">
                                    <tal:results tal:define="results python:collection.queryCatalog()"
                                            tal:condition="results">
                                        <h4>Socio-economic dimensions</h4>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li tal:repeat="result results">
                                                <a tal:attributes="href result/getURL">
                                                    <span tal:content="result/Title">Title</span>
                                                </a>
                                            </li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </tal:results>
                                </div>

                                <div class="eea-list-columns eea-three-columns"
                                        tal:define="collection python:context.restrictedTraverse('soer-2015/collections/systemic-perspectives', None);"
                                        tal:condition="nocall:collection">
                                    <tal:results tal:define="results python:collection.queryCatalog()"
                                            tal:condition="results">
                                        <h4>Systemic perspectives</h4>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li tal:repeat="result results">
                                                <a tal:attributes="href result/getURL">
                                                    <span tal:content="result/Title">Title</span>
                                                </a>
                                            </li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </tal:results>
                                </div>

                            </tal:europe>

                            <div class="eea-footer-right visualClear pull-right">
                                <div class="visualHidden">
                                    <div id="pdf-choice-europe">
                                        <span class="eea-icon eea-icon-download eea-icon-2x"></span> <a href="/soer-2015/europe/download.pdf">Download report (PDF)</a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="visualHidden">
                                    <div id="epub-choice-europe">
                                        <span class="eea-icon eea-icon-download eea-icon-2x"></span> <a href="/soer-2015/europe/action-download-epub">Download report (EPUB)</a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                 <p class="pull-left">Download all European briefings</p>
                                 <a class="download-pdf pull-left" href="/soer-2015/europe/download.pdf"  title="download PDF"><span class="eea-icon eea-icon-file-pdf-o eea-icon-2x"></span></a> <a class="download-epub pull-left fancybox" href="#epub-choice-europe"  title="download EPUB"><span class="eea-icon eea-icon-mobile-phone eea-icon-3x"></span></a>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="eea-tabs-panel">
                            <p>Cross-country comparisons provide an analysis of progress across European countries for selected topics. They are based on EEA and Eurostat indicators.</p>

                            <tal:countries-comparison tal:define="results python:cview.content(parent_id='soer-2015', object_id='countries-comparison')">
                                <ul>
                                    <li tal:repeat="result results">
                                        <a tal:attributes="href result/getURL">
                                            <span tal:content="result/title">Countries Comparison</span>
                                        </a>
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </tal:countries-comparison>

                            <div class="eea-footer-right visualClear pull-right">
                                <div class="visualHidden">
                                    <div id="pdf-choice-cross">
                                        <span class="eea-icon eea-icon-download eea-icon-2x"></span> <a href="/soer-2015/countries-comparison/download.pdf">Download report (PDF)</a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="visualHidden">
                                    <div id="epub-choice-cross">
                                        <span class="eea-icon eea-icon-download eea-icon-2x"></span> <a href="/soer-2015/countries-comparison/action-download-epub">Download report (EPUB)</a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                 <p class="pull-left">Download all cross-country comparisons</p>
                                 <a class="download-pdf pull-left" href="/soer-2015/countries-comparison/download.pdf"  title="download PDF"><span class="eea-icon eea-icon-file-pdf-o eea-icon-2x"></span></a> <a class="download-epub pull-left fancybox" href="#epub-choice-cross"  title="download EPUB"><span class="eea-icon eea-icon-mobile-phone eea-icon-3x"></span></a>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="eea-tabs-panel">
                            <p>Country briefings provide an overview of state of the environment across 39 European countries, based on national state of environment reports. Regional briefings cover three regions, identified as priority areas in the EU's 7th Environmental Action Programme.</p>
                            <h4>Countries briefings</h4>
                            <div tal:define="collection python:context.restrictedTraverse('soer-2015/collections/country-briefings', None);" tal:condition="nocall:collection">
                                <tal:results tal:define="results python:collection.queryCatalog(batch=False)"
                                        tal:condition="results">
                                    <tal:countries tal:define="results_length python:len(results);
                                                               ratio python: (results_length + 6) / 3;
                                                               double_ratio python: ratio * 2;">
                                        <ul class='eea-list-columns eea-three-columns'>
                                            <li tal:repeat="result python:results[:ratio]">
                                                <a tal:attributes="href result/getURL">
                                                    <span tal:content="result/Title">Title</span>
                                                </a>
                                            </li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <ul class='eea-list-columns eea-three-columns'>
                                            <li tal:repeat="result python:results[ratio:double_ratio]">
                                                <a tal:attributes="href result/getURL">
                                                    <span tal:content="result/Title">Title</span>
                                                </a>
                                            </li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <div class='eea-list-columns eea-three-columns'>
                                            <ul>
                                                <li tal:repeat="result python:results[double_ratio:]">
                                                    <a tal:attributes="href result/getURL">
                                                        <span tal:content="result/Title">Title</span>
                                                    </a>
                                                </li>
                                            </ul>

                                            <div tal:define="collection python:context.restrictedTraverse('soer-2015/collections/regional-briefings', None);"
                                                    tal:condition="nocall:collection">
                                                <h4>Regional briefings</h4>
                                                <ul tal:define="res python:collection.queryCatalog()">
                                                    <li tal:repeat="result res">
                                                        <a tal:attributes="href result/getURL">
                                                            <span tal:content="result/Title">Title</span>
                                                        </a>
                                                    </li>
                                                </ul>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </tal:countries>
                                </tal:results>
                            </div>
                            <div class="pull-left"><p class="discreet" style="margin-top:0.5em;">*under the UN SCR 1244/99</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="eea-footer-right visualClear pull-right">
                                <div class="visualHidden">
                                    <div id="pdf-choice-countries">
                                        <span class="eea-icon eea-icon-download eea-icon-2x"></span> <a href="/soer-2015/countries/download.pdf">Download report (PDF)</a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="visualHidden">
                                    <div id="epub-choice-countries">
                                        <span class="eea-icon eea-icon-download eea-icon-2x"></span> <a href="/soer-2015/countries/action-download-epub">Download report (EPUB)</a>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                 <p class="pull-left">Download all countries and regions</p>
                                 <a class="download-pdf pull-left" href="/soer-2015/countries/download.pdf"  title="download PDF"><span class="eea-icon eea-icon-file-pdf-o eea-icon-2x"></span></a> <a class="download-epub pull-left fancybox" href="#epub-choice-countries" title="download EPUB"><span class="eea-icon eea-icon-mobile-phone eea-icon-3x"></span></a>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                    </div>
                    <!--? eea-tabs-panels -->
                </div>
                <div class="right-column-area">
                    <dl class="portlet portletStaticText portlet-static-help">

                        <dt class="portletHeader">
                        <span class="portletTopLeft"></span>
                        <span>
                            SOER 2015 — EXPLORE
                        </span>
                        <span class="portletTopRight"></span>
                        </dt>
                        <dd class="portletItem odd">
                        <a href="/soer-2015/explore-quick-facts-and-figures" title="Explore SOER 2015 via an interactive presentation (PDF)">
                           <img width="100%" height="200px" src="http://www.eea.europa.eu/soer-2015/soer-explore-image/image_preview">
                        </a>
                        </dd>
                        <dd class="portletItem odd" style="margin-top:0.5em;">
                        <!-- optional description to soer explore -->
                        <a href="/soer-2015/explore-quick-facts-and-figures" title="Explore SOER 2015 via an interactive presentation (PDF)"><span class="eea-icon eea-icon-file-pdf-o"></span>Download the SOER 2015 presentation (PDF)</a>
                        </dd>
                    </dl>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!--? END Tabbed navigation -->
        <!--? Gallery & Navigation -->
        <div class="lower-highlights">
            <!--? Key facts -->
            <div class="eea-row">
                <div class="column-area">


            <div id="boxes">
                <div metal:define-macro="keyfacts-slider"
                    tal:define="background_img_path background_img_path| python: context.getCanonical().absolute_url() + '/image_large'  "
                     id="keyfacts-slider" class="figure keyFactsSlider">
                       <div class="keyfactsImgContainer"><img class="keyfacts-bgimg" src=""
                        tal:attributes="src background_img_path"  /></div>
                       <div  tal:define="items context/soer2015_getAllKeyFacts">
                            <div id="soer-top-area">
                                <!-- all key facts and messages -->
                                <dl
                                    class="portlet slidePortlet" >
                                    <dt class="portletHeader" style="padding:5px;" i18n:translate=""><a href="/soer-2015/collections/all-key-messages" style="color:white;" title="see all key messages">Key messages</a></dt>
                                     <dd class="portletItem" style="left: 650px;" tal:repeat="item items">
                                       <span>
                                          <a href="" title="Read more of the key fact"
                                              class="moreLink link-plain" style="font-size:100%;"
                                              tal:attributes="href item/parent_url;title item/parent_title;"
                                              i18n:attributes="title"
                                              i18n:translate="" tal:content="item/parent_title">more</a>:&nbsp;
                                          <span tal:replace="structure item/text"></span>
                                          <a href="" title="Read more of the key fact"
                                              class="moreLink link-plain" style="font-size:100%;"
                                              tal:attributes="href item/parent_url;title item/parent_title;"
                                              i18n:attributes="title"
                                              i18n:translate="">See briefing</a>
                                        </span>
                                     </dd>
                                </dl>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                 </div>
                </div>
                </div> <!--? END Key facts -->

                <!--? Navigation portlet-->
                <div class="right-column-area">
                    <dl class="portlet portletNavigationTree">
                        <dt class="portletHeader" id="firstHeader">
                        <a tal:attributes="href string:$portal_url/soer-2015">SOER 2015 - The European environment -
                            State and Outlook</a>
                        </dt>
                        <dt class="portletSubMenuHeader">
                        <span class="title eea-icon-right-container">Menu</span>
                        </dt>
                        <dd class="portletItem lastItem">
                        <ul class="navTree navTreeLevel0">
                            <li class="navTreeItem visualNoMarker navTreeFolderish section-global">
                            <a tal:attributes="href string:$portal_url/soer-2015/about"
                                class=" navTreeFolderish contenttype-folder" title="">
                                <span>About SOER 2015</span>
                            </a>
                            </li>
                            <li class="navTreeItem visualNoMarker navTreeFolderish section-europe">
                            <a tal:attributes="href string:$portal_url/soer-2015/for-journalists"
                                class=" navTreeFolderish contenttype-folder" title="">
                                <span>For journalists</span>
                            </a>
                            </li>
                            <li class="navTreeItem visualNoMarker navTreeFolderish section-countries-comparison">
                            <a tal:attributes="href string:$portal_url/soer-2015/events"
                                class=" navTreeFolderish contenttype-folder" title="">
                                <span>Events</span>
                            </a>
                            </li>
                            <li class="navTreeItem visualNoMarker navTreeFolderish section-countries">
                            <a tal:attributes="href string:$portal_url/soer-2015/feedback"
                                class=" navTreeFolderish contenttype-folder" title="">
                                <span>Feedback</span>
                            </a>
                            </li>
                            <li class="navTreeItem visualNoMarker navTreeFolderish section-progress-monitoring">
                            <a tal:attributes="href string:$portal_url/soer-2015/photos-and-videos"
                                class=" navTreeFolderish contenttype-folder" title="">
                                <span>Photos and videos</span>
                            </a>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                        </dd>
                    </dl>
                </div>
                <div class="right-column-area pull-right">
                    <dl id="portlet-followus">
                        <dt class="portletHeader">Follow us</dt>
                        <dd>
                        <a id="twitter-link" title="Follow us on Twitter" href="http://twitter.com/euenvironment">&nbsp;</a>
                        </dd>
                        <dd>
                        <a id="facebook-link" title="Follow us on Facebook" href="http://www.facebook.com/European.Environment.Agency">&nbsp;</a>
                        </dd>
                        <dd>
                        <a id="youtube-link" title="Follow us on YouTube" href="http://www.youtube.com/user/EEAvideos">&nbsp;</a>
                        </dd>
                        <dd>
                        <a id="rss-link" title="Subscribe to RSS Feed" class="link-plain" tal:attributes="href string:$portal_url/subscription/news-feeds">&nbsp;</a>
                        </dd>
                        <dd>
                        <a id="email-link" title="Subscribe by email" href="#subscribe-popup" class="fancybox">&nbsp;</a>
                        </dd>
                    </dl>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!--? END Gallery & Navigation -->

<!-- Next div is used by the PDF async mailer popup -->
<div class="eea-pdf-viewlet" data-async="1"></div>
</metal:content-core>
</metal:content-core>
</body>
</html>